{"tid":2390780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（轉貼）攪到今時今日封區，係香港人自己要求既","createTime":"2021-02-01T20:19:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T05:00:32.000Z","uid":131157,"like":9,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"463dfe5af7dd64827c7f31a52c22feaa2497b717","tid":2390780,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T20:19:29.000Z","msg":"【家必自毀而後人毀之】<br />\n<strong>係你哋自己去翻查衞生署準則、出圖列哂啲大廈資料做特寫、引埋專家話要「願檢盡檢」，指政府太慢、強檢得唔夠多㗎嘛。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>傳媒好專業㗎嘛，啲政論好透徹㗎嘛，你哋而家先知呢個係港共政府？示威就去捉鬼，強檢就去捉人，映大頭相、直播逃生、詳列名單，成功爭取係咪覺得好好玩？<br />\n</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟我講一次：<br />\n<br />\n檢疫方艙，係香港人自己起嘅！<br />\n檢疫捉人，係香港人自己捉嘅！<br />\n檢疫強制，係香港人自己要嘅！<br />\n<br />\n全部都係香港人自己做嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>BTW，垃場嗰篇大廈特寫名單出咗兩次，慌你睇唔到。</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#自己手足自己捉<br />\n#自己頭家自己封<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/349165895166373/posts/3682995495116713/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F349165895166373%2Fposts%2F3682995495116713%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl7tFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=d69cade7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/349165895166373/posts/3682995495116713/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"ef0ff17330c72c4d7b606134a5522957fb1f66fd","tid":2390780,"uid":131157,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T20:23:42.000Z","msg":"香港幾時所謂既「疫情」會完結呢？<br />\n班垃圾傳媒收檔果一日就係"},{"pid":"07